{"word":"H2266 - חָבַר - châbar - khaw-bar' - Charm","slug":"H2266","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָבַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>châbar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khaw-bar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Charm"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05D1;&#x05E8; - cha&#x0302;bar</b> - <i>khaw-bar'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>join</i> (literally or figuratively); specifically (by means of spells) to <i>fascinate: - </i>charm (-er), be compact, couple (together), have fellowship with, heap up, join (self, together), league."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2249\">H2249</a>, <a href=\"#/H2250\">H2250</a>, <a href=\"#/H2267\">H2267</a>, <a href=\"#/H2268\">H2268</a>, <a href=\"#/H2270\">H2270</a>, <a href=\"#/H2271\">H2271</a>, <a href=\"#/H2272\">H2272</a>, <a href=\"#/H2274\">H2274</a>, <a href=\"#/H2275\">H2275</a>, <a href=\"#/H2276\">H2276</a>, <a href=\"#/H2277\">H2277</a>, <a href=\"#/H2278\">H2278</a>, <a href=\"#/H2279\">H2279</a>, <a href=\"#/H4225\">H4225</a>, <a href=\"#/H4226\">H4226</a>"}]}